{"tid":2511660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港就應該俾大陸同化","createTime":"2021-05-01T05:37:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T05:37:12.000Z","uid":167915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e8e90a75cd7a05828a22375f63ae35726d37ce15","tid":2511660,"uid":167915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T05:37:12.000Z","msg":"見到呢個post不期然有呢個諗法<br />\n<br />\n普京簽署新法令 可讓其再連任兩屆以及宣佈同性戀為非法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2511494\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2511494</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家睇到個標題第一下有咩諗法<br />\n小弟第一下係諗緊極權國家又勝一仗<br />\n終身制好似傳染病咁 可能好多極權國家黎緊都想玩呢招 <br />\n本身以為個post 想係呢方面有多啲討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但睇下睇下 發現同性戀先係被討論既重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過理解到呢到係兒登<br />\n講同性戀 基本上係一面倒既聲音 都唔需要多講<br />\n其實大陸係呢方面都有唔錯既成就<br />\n做咩仲走去反共<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反正大家既陰暗面都係要<span class=\"red\">抨擊 傷害 抵制 侮辱 恥笑 維護既得利益 </span> 等等等等<br />\n<br />\n大家既真實一面同共產黨係無咩分別架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暗地都係blue and red object <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n距離大中華時代又近一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}